WORKING CODE
============

   R   (as.data.frame was not obvious to me)
   ==
   want<-as.data.frame(have %>%
     group_by(IMG) %>%
     mutate(ELAPSEDTIME = TIME - first(TIME) + 1));

   SAS
   ===
    by img;
    select;
      when ( first.img ) do;
         elapsedTime=time;
         tym1st=time;
      end;
      otherwise
         elapsedTime=time-tym1st+1;
    end;


